Skills to Enjoy
When you [learn] or [produce] something, you often have to [spend] a lot of time.

Whether one perceives this "lots of time" fragment as "[effort]" and "[hard work]" or "[fun]" and "[interesting]" is [individual subjectivity].

Those who perceive it as "[fun]" are more likely to succeed in "[spending] a lot of time on it."

